## project description
# to use liquibase (an open source database independent library to tract all database related activities)

## Project configuration

# 2 profiles 
@ 1. mysql profile to execute scripts in mysql database
@ 2. oracle profile to execute scripts in Oracle database

# execute mysql 
	
	mvn -Denv=mysql liquibase:dropAll : drop all the records in mysql database
	mvn -Denv=mysql liquibase:update : update all the records in mysql database
	
# execute oracle 
	
	mvn -Denv=oracle liquibase:dropAll : drop all the records in oracle database
	mvn -Denv=oracle liquibase:update : update all the records in oracle database
	
	